Cdata.Note: Bastard Son of the Holy Empire. Vale is the family name of his mother taking it for his own protection as he is kept hidden from the public as he is Half Elf. Even with his clear hatred from the People of the Castle he maintains the worship to their god and remains loyal to the Church. While he is 15, a rogue servant would reveal the secret of the young prince to the Public which caused him to flee and would later be sent to Freedom Academy.

From a very young age, she was born into a simple, impoverished family, where she had to toil hard every day to contribute towards putting meals on the table. Life was incredibly challenging, but the love of her parents provided some solace. Although not without flaws, her parents were the best she could have asked for. However, tragedy struck the family when they fell ill. Despite managing to arrange medicine for her, they didn't have enough for themselves and tragically succumbed to the illness, all the while wearing smiles as they watched over their surviving daughter.
